These software tests depend on the following:

1) util/nccmp.py, which depends on the netCDF3 module from the netcdf4-python
package (see http://code.google.com/p/netcdf4-python/) and numpy.
2) NetCDF Operators (NCO), see http://nco.sourceforge.net/


*** To run all PISM tests, do

$ ./run_tests.sh pism

or simply 

$ make

The summary will be in the file "pism.txt".

*** To run an individual PISM test, (test 1, for example) do

$ cd pism; ./test_01.sh

